# Security Baseline

## Input
- Zod validation on all external input
- Integer pence only; no float for money

## Secrets
- No secrets in client code
- Use env vars; document in .env.example
- Never log tokens, emails, passwords

## API
- Rate limit /api/save and /api/saved
- CSRF: Auth.js handles for auth routes
- Security headers in middleware

## Database
- Prisma ORM (parameterized queries)
- Scope by userId for user data
